         <abstract>
            <p>For the method and problems under consideration we estimate the error in the maximum norm as well as at individual nodal points. In order to obtain full superconvergence at all nodal points we have to introduce local mesh refinements, even though the exact solution is smooth for the given class of problems.</p>
          </abstract>
